name: Submersible Nuclear Void
text:
3 "Submersible" Monsters
(Quick Effect) You can banish this face-up card until the End Phase; Special Summon 2 "Torpedo Tokens" (Machine-Type/WATER/Level 3/ATK 1500/DEF 1500). These tokens cannot be used for a Link Summon. If this card is in the banished zone because it was sent there this turn by its own effect (Quick Effect): You can tribute 1 "Torpedo Token" you control and target 1 card on the field; destroy it.
